      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, love the 'jaundiced' thing. can we get a bit more specific though? i need to describe the actual people on the street to really ground the tension. like, what kind of people are hanging out on these corners, what are they wearing, what do they look like when they see a stranger walking through? i want to make it feel authentic to a really rough, high-crime area.",
